data = csv.reader(f)

    if row[-1] != '' :
        if row[0].split('-')[1] == '08' :
            result.append(float(row[-1]))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.plot(result, 'hotpink')
plt.show()

data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
high = []
low = []

for row in data :
    if row[-1] != '' and row[-2] != '' :
        if row[0].split('-')[1] == '02' and row[0].split('-')[2] == '14' :
            high.append(float(row[-1]))
            low.append(float(row[-2]))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt.plot(low, 'skyblue')

import csv
f = open('seoul_temp.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
high = []
low = []

for row in data :
    if row[-1] != '' and row[-2] != '' :
        if 1983 <= int(row[0].split('-')[0]) :
            if row[0].split('-')[1] == '02' and row[0].split('-')[2] == '14' :
                high.append(float(row[-1]))
                low.append(float(row[-2]))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.rc('font', family = 'Malgun Gothic')
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False
plt.title('내 생일의 기온 변화 그래프')
plt.plot(high, 'hotpink', label = 'high')
plt.plot(low, 'skyblue', label = 'low')
plt.legend()
plt.show()

import csv
f = open('seoul_temp.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
high = []
low = []

for row in data :
    if row[-1] != '' and row[-2] != '' :
        date = row[0].split('-')
        if 1983 <= int(date[0]) :

                high.append(float(row[-1]))
                low.append(float(row[-2]))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

In [23]:
import csv
f = open('seoul_temp.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
high = []
low = []
year = []

for row in data :
    if row[-1] != '' and row[-2] != '' :
        date = row[0].split('-')
        if 1983 <= int(date[0]) :
            if date[1] == '02' and date[2] == '14' :
                high.append(float(row[-1]))
                low.append(float(row[-2]))
                year.append(int(date[0]))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.rc('font', family = 'Malgun Gothic')
plt.title('내 생일의 기온 변화 그래프')
plt.plot(high, 'hotpink')
plt.plot(low, 'skyblue')
plt.xticks(range(len(year)), year)
plt.show()
In [24]:
import csv
f = open('seoul_temp.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
high = []
low = []
year = []

for row in data :
    if row[-1] != '' and row[-2] != '' :
        date = row[0].split('-')
        if 1983 <= int(date[0]) :
            if date[1] == '02' and date[2] == '14' :
                high.append(float(row[-1]))
                low.append(float(row[-2]))
                year.append(int(date[0]))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.rc('font', family = 'Malgun Gothic')
plt.title('내 생일의 기온 변화 그래프')
plt.plot(high, 'hotpink', label = 'high')
plt.plot(low, 'skyblue', label = 'low')
plt.xticks(range(0,len(year),5), year[::5])
plt.legend()
plt.show()
In [25]:
import csv
f = open('seoul_temp.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
result = []

for row in data :
    if row[-1] != '' and row[-2] != '' :
        if 1983 <= int(row[0].split('-')[0]) :
            if row[0].split('-')[1] == '02' and row[0].split('-')[2] == '14' :
                result.append(float(row[-1]) - float(-2))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.rc('font', family = 'Malgun Gothic')
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False
plt.title('내 생일의 일교차 변화 그래프')
plt.plot(result, 'forestgreen')
plt.xticks(range(0,len(year),5), year[::5])
plt.show()
In [26]:
import csv
f = open('seoul_temp.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
result = []

for row in data :
    if row[-1] != '' and row[-2] != '' :
        if 1983 <= int(row[0].split('-')[0]) :
            if row[0].split('-')[1] == '02' and row[0].split('-')[2] == '14' :
                result.append(float(row[-1]) - float(-2))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.rc('font', family = 'Malgun Gothic')
plt.title('내 생일의 일교차 변화 그래프')
plt.bar(range(len(result)), result, color = 'forestgreen')
plt.xticks(range(0,len(year),5), year[::5])
plt.show()
